channel.title: 86 Nissan
channel.description:
So I paid 1500 for a 1986 Nissan TX "Hardbody Pickup" d21 When i bought it, It had no engine in it no clutch or tranny The engine came with it.. "Brand new crate v6" it has a 4 inch lift 31/10/50 mudding tires, and the clutch is like 80$ I ordered a clutch and the tranny was in the back got it all back together top speed was "115" with a quarter of throttle left.. dual cherry bombs... I'll take a picture tomorrow is it a good find and it took me 3 days to get it put together..
3.0L..V6
